@startuml
title Klassendiagramm - Homelab Service Dashboard

class Service {
  +id: string
  +name: string
  +type: string
  +target: string
  +host: string
  +port: int
  +categoryId: string
  +lastStatus: string
  +lastCheckedAt: string
}

class Category {
  +id: string
  +name: string
  +color: string
}

class CheckResult {
  +id: string
  +serviceId: string
  +checkedAt: string
  +online: boolean
  +statusCode: int
  +responseTimeMs: int
  +message: string
}

Service "0..*" --> "1" Category : gehört zu
Service "1" --> "0..*" CheckResult : erzeugt

@enduml